headline: Williams-Sonoma, Inc. declares quarterly cash dividend
summary: SAN FRANCISCO, December 12, 2024--Williams-Sonoma, Inc. (NYSE: WSM) announced today that its Board of Directors has declared a quarterly cash dividend of $0.57 per share of common stock. Each stockholder of record as of the close of business on January 17, 2025 will be paid the cash dividend on February 21, 2025.

headline: RH price target raised to $435 from $384 at BofA
summary: BofA raised the firm’s price target on RH (RH) to $435 from $384 and keeps a Buy rating on the shares. Ahead of the company’s Q3 report due on December 12, the firm notes it projects revenue and EPS of $817M and $2.81, respectively, 0.6% and 7% above the Street forecasts.
